// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
//  POLICY (what this spec ALLOWS and FORBIDS)
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
//
//   ALLOWED effects: FileRead, FileWrite, ProcessList (ps read-only),
//                    SysControl (sysctl read-only), Clock
//
//   FORBIDDEN effects (prime directive):
//     ProcessKill, ProcessThrottle (taskpolicy/SIGSTOP/renice),
//     MemoryPurge, CompressorTune, SystemWrite
//
//   Efficiency gains come from smarter data movement at interface gates,
//   not from controlling processes.

